title: Eight Skiers Killed, One Missing in California Avalanche
description: Eight skiers were found dead after being trapped by an avalanche in the mountains of northern California. Another is missing and presumed dead. It happened close to Lake Tahoe. This is Nevada County Sheriff Shannan Moon. (Source: Bloomberg)
